DDM test case: scattering by a sphere, domain is split into concentric
spheres.

Set parameters in params.geo ; other parameters (mostly advanced
parameters for the DDM transmission conditions) are available in
sphere_concentric.pro.


- Generate the mesh (both full and split meshes):
  gmsh sphere_concentric_mshcut.geo -

- Compute full solution (select Maxwell_Lagrange):
  getdp sphere_concentric.pro -sol -pos -bin

- Compute DDM solution
  getdp sphere_concentric.pro -sol DDM -v 0 -bin -ksp_monitor

- View solutions:
  gmsh combine_e_vol.geo
  gmsh combine_e_vol_tot.geo
